OL,3,COne ketamine-related death 'a week' in
OL,4,CUK amid fears of 'next drug pandemic'
OL,6,FDeaths related to ketamine are up 650%
OL,7,Fsince 2015, with new figures showing
OL,8,Fone death 'each week' involving the
OL,9,Fdrug across the UK.
OL,11,FExperts have warned the drug is taking
OL,12,Fthe lives of people right across the
OL,13,Fcountry and say it could be the next
OL,14,F'drug pandemic'.
OL,16,FFigures obtained by a Freedom of
OL,17,FInformation Request, and seen
OL,18,Fexclusively by ITV News, highlights
OL,19,Fthe growing problem around the Class B
OL,20,Fdrug.
