OL,3,COne ketamine-related death 'a week' in
OL,4,CUK amid fears of 'next drug pandemic'
OL,6,FData released by the Office for
OL,7,FNational Statistics (ONS) and obtained
OL,8,Fby The UKAT Group show three times as
OL,9,Fmany women are losing their lives to
OL,10,Fthe drug since before the Covid
OL,11,Fpandemic, with deaths from those under
OL,12,F30 years old involving the drug seeing
OL,13,Fa 300% rise in as many years.
OL,15,FThe statistics show where the drug has
OL,16,Fbeen listed on a person's death
OL,17,Fcertificate.
OL,19,FDeath certificate data from 2024
OL,20,Fonwards is yet to be released.
