OL,6,FWhat is ketamine?
OL,8,FKetamine is an anaesthetic horse
OL,9,Ftranquilliser that has hallucinogenic
OL,10,Feffects.
OL,12,FIt distorts perceptions of sight and
OL,13,Fsound and makes the user feel
OL,14,Fdisconnected and not in control.
OL,16,FAlong with the other "club drugs" it
OL,17,Fhas become popular among teens and
OL,18,Fyoung adults and is manufactured
OL,19,Fcommercially as a powder or liquid and
OL,20,Fcan be snorted or swallowed.
