OL,6,FShort-term effects can include memory
OL,7,Floss, impaired judgement,
OL,8,Fdisorientation, clumsiness and anxiety
OL,10,FRegular users may experience
OL,11,Fflashbacks, mood and personality
OL,12,Fchanges, depression, concentration
OL,13,Fproblems and abdominal pain.
OL,15,FAn overdose can cause unconsciousness
OL,16,Fand dangerously slowed breathing, and
OL,17,Fin some cases, death.
