OL,6,FKetamine is currently controlled as a
OL,7,FClass B substance and the maximum
OL,8,Fpenalty for supplying and producing it
OL,9,Fis up to 14 years in prison, an
OL,10,Funlimited fine, or both.
OL,12,FThe UKAT Group's analysis, seen
OL,13,Fexclusively by ITV News shows that in
OL,14,F2015, just seven people across England
OL,15,Fand Wales lost their lives where
OL,16,FKetamine was involved. The latest data
OL,17,Fshows this has risen by 650%, with 53
OL,18,Flives lost in 2023.
