OL,6,FThe results show that every year
OL,7,Fexcept 2019 saw a steady rise in the
OL,8,Fnumber of people losing their lives
OL,9,Fwhere Ketamine was involved.
OL,11,FThe worst year for teenage deaths
OL,12,Fwhere Ketamine was mentioned on the
OL,13,Fdeath certificate was in 2021, where
OL,14,Ffour people aged 15-19 lost their
OL,15,Flives. According to The UKAT Group's
OL,16,Fanalysis, all four of those teenagers
OL,17,Fwere male.
