OL,6,FThe region with the highest number of
OL,7,Fregistered deaths where Ketamine was
OL,8,Fmentioned in 2023 was the South East
OL,9,Fwith seven deaths.
OL,11,FThe Government announced in January it
OL,12,Fwould seek expert advice on
OL,13,Freclassifying ketamine to become a
OL,14,FClass A substance, alongside the likes
OL,15,Fof cocaine and ecstasy, after illegal
OL,16,Fuse of the drug reached record levels
OL,17,Fin the year ending March 2023.
