OL,6,FIt can cause serious health problems,
OL,7,Fsuch as irreversible damage to the
OL,8,Fbladder and kidneys, and is one of the
OL,9,Fmost detected drugs in incidents of
OL,10,Fspiking.
OL,12,FRecent reports have shown Ketamine is
OL,13,Foften an ingredient included in 'pink
OL,14,Fcocaine', the dangerous synthetic drug
OL,15,Fcocktail taken by users without
OL,16,Fknowing what mix of substances it
OL,17,Fcontains.
