OL,6,FZaheen Ahmed, Director of Addiction
OL,7,FTherapy at the UKAT Group which treats
OL,8,Fpeople over 18 for Ketamine addiction
OL,9,Fcomments on the findings have called
OL,10,Fon the government to act.
OL,12,F"Ketamine deaths are rising and they
OL,13,Fshouldn't be, it's as simple as that",
OL,14,Fexplains Ahmed.
OL,16,F"This is a drug that has flown under
OL,17,Fthe radar for far too long.
